title: KUT from the Kloth Reese High-Rise Fab AB Ankle Straight Raw Hem in Relieve
description: A go-to for endless casual looks, these slim-cut straight-leg jeans feature light distressing, raw hems and signature Fab Ab front pockets.

Look basic yet chic by wearing the KUT from the Kloth Reese High-Rise Fab AB Ankle Straight Raw Hem in Relieve Jeans. High-rise, straight-cut fit. Zip-fly and button closure. Classic five-pocket design. Brand name logo on the back waist. Slight distress. Raw edge hems. 67% cotton, 30% REPREVE, 2% viscose, 1% spandex. Machine washable. Measurements:Inseam: 27 in.
